author: Kashmira Gander
title: The Dire Consequences of Stopping Social Distancing During Spread of Coronavirus Explained
description: There is currently no treatment or vaccine for the new coronavirus which causes COVID-19.
content:
A top expert in pandemics at Johns Hopkins University has warned against ending social distancing in the U.S. too soon, as the country continues to try to control the spread of COVID-19.
